        | 1234
      .notes.injury.col-md-1.col-xs-1
        | Injury
      .notes.call.col-md-1.col-xs-1
        | Call
      .notes.lost.col-md-1.col-xs-1
        | Lost
      .points.col-md-1.col-xs-1
        | 10
